channel.title: Help Please
channel.description:
Hello. i was coding off the cloudin source and ive had it for awhile and everything was fine. i went to restart the source to see if the stuff i added worked. which it has in the past. but today after i compiled and tryed to run the server i got this error.
[code][2012/02/10 10:49:16] [Server]: rs2hd framework [2012/02/10 10:49:16] [Server]: Loaded 15577 item prices. Exception in thread "Server" java.lang.ExceptionInInitializerError at com.rs2hd.Server.<init>(Server.java:71) at com.rs2hd.Main$1.run(Main.java:36) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source) Caused by: java.lang.NullPointerException at com.rs2hd.model.NoclipHandler.<init>(NoclipHandler.java:80) at com.rs2hd.GameEngine.<clinit>(GameEngine.java:112) ... 3 more Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Please Help me!
